name: Victory
description:
In order to welcome the launch of the V mainnet, create a core community currency, and welcome all the ground communities of the V system to enter the V network, the token VIC is hereby issued.
VIC is the first commemorative coin of the V main network. It carries the expectations of the V system family for many years, and is also a bridge between the V network and the external network.
The mission of VIC is to let users know about the V main network, the core operating currency of the cross-chain bridge
